com.teamdev.jxbrowser.chromium.dom

Interface DOMDocument

  • All Superinterfaces:
    SearchContext 

    public interface DOMDocument
extends SearchContext
    Represents DOM HTML document of the web page.
    表示网页的DOM HTML文档。

    • Method Detail

      • getDocumentElement

        DOMElement getDocumentElement()
        Returns the document HTML element that usually represents HTML tag. This method can return null if document element is not available (e.g. the web page of this document was disposed).
        返回通常表示HTML标签的文档HTML元素。如果文档元素不可用（例如，放置了此文档的网页），则此方法可以返回null。
        Returns:
        the document HTML element that usually represents HTML tag or null if document element is not available. 通常表示HTML标记或如果文档元素不可用的文档HTML元素。

      • createElement

        DOMElement createElement(java.lang.String tagName)
        Creates and returns a new DOM element with the specified tag name.
        创建并返回具有指定标签名称的新DOM元素。
        Parameters:
        tagName - the tag name (e.g. "A", "P", "DIV") of the new DOM element. -新DOM元素的标签名称（例如“ A”，“ P”，“ DIV”）。
        Returns:
        the new DOMElement or null if tagName is wrong. 新的或如果是错误的。
        Throws:
        java.lang.IllegalArgumentException - when tagName parameter is empty or null.

      • createEvent

        DOMEvent createEvent(DOMEventType eventType,
                     DOMEventParams params)
        Creates a new DOMEvent object with the given eventType and params. The event object can be dispatched at specific DOMEventTarget using the DOMEventTarget.dispatchEvent(DOMEvent) method.
        使用给定的eventType和params创建一个新的DOMEvent对象。可以使用DOMEventTarget.dispatchEvent（DOMEvent）方法在特定的DOMEventTarget上调度事件对象。
        Parameters:
        eventType - the DOM event type. Cannot be null. -DOM事件类型。不可能是 。
        params - the parameters of the event. Cannot be null. -事件的参数。不可能是 。
        Returns:
        a new DOMEvent object. 一个新的对象。
        Throws:
        DOMException - when document fails to create DOM event.
        Since:
        6.13

      • createKeyEvent

        DOMKeyEvent createKeyEvent(DOMEventType eventType,
                           DOMKeyEventParams params)
        Creates a new DOMKeyEvent object with the given eventType and params. The event object can be dispatched at specific DOMEventTarget using the DOMEventTarget.dispatchEvent(DOMEvent) method.

        Important: it's strongly recommended that the OnKeyDown, OnKeyUp, and OnKeyPress event types are used when creating DOM key event. With other event types, Chromium engine might fail to create DOM key event and throw DOMException.

        使用给定的eventType和params创建一个新的DOMKeyEvent对象。可以使用DOMEventTarget.dispatchEvent（DOMEvent）方法在特定的DOMEventTarget上调度事件对象。重要说明：强烈建议在创建DOM键事件时使用OnKeyDown，OnKeyUp和OnKeyPress事件类型。对于其他事件类型，Chromium引擎可能无法创建DOM键事件并抛出DOMException。
        Parameters:
        eventType - the DOM event type. Cannot be null. -DOM事件类型。不可能是 。
        params - the parameters of the event. Cannot be null. -事件的参数。不可能是 。
        Returns:
        a new DOMKeyEvent object. 一个新的对象。
        Throws:
        DOMException - when document fails to create DOM event.
        Since:
        6.13

      • getBaseURI

        java.lang.String getBaseURI()
        Returns the absolute base URL of the document
        返回文档的绝对基础URL
        Returns:
      • value of <base> element's href attribute if one is present
      • otherwise, currently loaded location (including "about:blank" value for the case when nothing is loaded)
